---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Photography Packages & Pricing — Dallas TX"
description: "Transparent photography packages for quinceañeras, sweet 16s, proms, graduations, and portraits in Dallas, Texas. Book Pichardo's Photography today."
ogImage: /assets/img/gallery/xv/aleyah-xv-1.JPEG
---

{% block schema %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Photography Packages & Pricing",
  "description": "Photography package pricing for quinceañeras, sweet 16s, proms, and portraits in Dallas TX.",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/packages/",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Packages", "item": "{{ site.url }}/packages/" }
    ]
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>›</span> <span>Packages</span>
    </nav>
    <span class="eyebrow">Investment</span>
    <h1>Photography Packages</h1>
    <div class="gold-line center"></div>
    <p style="max-width:620px;margin:1rem auto 0;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.05rem;">
      Transparent pricing. No surprises. Every package delivers Miguel's signature editing and a private online gallery you'll treasure forever.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="packages-grid">

      <div class="package-card reveal">
        <div class="package-tier">Essential</div>
        <div class="package-name">The Classic</div>
        <div class="package-price">$350</div>
        <div class="package-price-note">Starting from · Portrait sessions</div>
        <ul class="package-features">
          <li>Up to 2 hours of coverage</li>
          <li>1 location / setting</li>
          <li>75+ edited digital images</li>
          <li>Private online gallery</li>
          <li>High-resolution downloads</li>
          <li>Personal use printing rights</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/?pkg=classic" class="btn btn-gold-outline" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Book Classic</a>
        <p class="package-note">Great for portraits, headshots, graduation mini-sessions</p>
      </div>

      <div class="package-card featured reveal" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="package-badge">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="package-tier">Signature</div>
        <div class="package-name">The Signature</div>
        <div class="package-price">$650</div>
        <div class="package-price-note">Starting from · Milestones &amp; events</div>
        <ul class="package-features">
          <li>Up to 4 hours of coverage</li>
          <li>2 locations included</li>
          <li>150+ edited digital images</li>
          <li>Private online gallery</li>
          <li>High-resolution downloads</li>
          <li>Pre-shoot style consultation</li>
          <li>Rush delivery available</li>
          <li>Print release included</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/?pkg=signature" class="btn btn-gold" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Book Signature</a>
        <p class="package-note">Perfect for prom, sweet 16, graduation, senior portraits</p>
      </div>

      <div class="package-card reveal" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="package-tier">Elite</div>
        <div class="package-name">The Elite</div>
        <div class="package-price">$1,200</div>
        <div class="package-price-note">Starting from · Full events</div>
        <ul class="package-features">
          <li>Full-day coverage (up to 8 hrs)</li>
          <li>Unlimited locations</li>
          <li>300+ edited digital images</li>
          <li>Private online gallery</li>
          <li>High-resolution downloads</li>
          <li>Pre-shoot consultation</li>
          <li>Commercial use license</li>
          <li>Priority 7-day editing turnaround</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/?pkg=elite" class="btn btn-gold-outline" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Book Elite</a>
        <p class="package-note">Ideal for quinceañeras, sweet 16 parties, full-day events</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Custom note -->
    <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:3rem;text-align:center;padding:2.5rem;background:var(--dark-card);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Custom Quotes</span>
      <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Need Something Tailored?</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Quinceañeras, weddings, multi-city events, and commercial projects all receive personalized quotes. Reach out and tell us about your vision — we'll build a package around your needs and budget.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-gold">Get a Custom Quote</a>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ mini -->
    <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:5rem;max-width:760px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <span class="eyebrow">Pricing FAQ</span>
        <h2>Common Questions</h2>
        <div class="gold-line center"></div>
      </div>

      <details>
        <summary>What's included in every package?</summary>
        <p>Every package includes Miguel's signature editing style, a private online gallery, and high-resolution downloads with personal printing rights. No hidden fees.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I reserve my date?</summary>
        <p>A deposit secures your date. Dates are not held until a deposit is received. Contact us to check availability for your event date.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How long until I receive my photos?</summary>
        <p>Standard turnaround is 3–6 weeks depending on the package and event size. Rush delivery (7–14 days) is available on Signature and Elite packages.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you travel outside Dallas?</summary>
        <p>Yes — we serve all of Texas. Travel fees may apply for locations outside the DFW Metroplex. Contact us for a quote that includes your city.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you offer payment plans?</summary>
        <p>Yes. We offer flexible payment plans for larger packages. A deposit holds your date and the balance is split into payments leading up to your event.</p>
      </details>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="banner">
  {% pic "/assets/img/gallery/prom/prom-10.JPEG", "", { class: "banner-bg", widths: [1400], sizes: "100vw", ariaHidden: true } %}
  <div class="banner-content container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Limited Dates Available</span>
      <h2>Book Before Your Date Is Gone</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);max-width:560px;margin:1rem auto 2rem;">
        Spring and fall fill up months in advance. Check availability today.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-gold">Check My Date</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
